STATE
v.
Timothy C. AUTRY. No. 482P05. Supreme Court of North Carolina. October 6, 2005. William P. Hart, Special Deputy Attorney General, G. Dewey Hudson, District Attorney, for State of NC.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 30th day of August 2005 by Defendant for Writ:

"Motion Denied by order of the Court in conference this the 6th day of October 2005."
